snippet.textDisplay:
Climate control programs have disrupted normal weather patterns which are now practically non existent.Aerosol spraying in the ozone layer is heating the earth fast.The polar melting is caused by these artificial weather . Temperatures have been pushed way out of normal on both ends.
"Geoengineering has created short term toxic cool-downs at the cost of an even worse overall long term planetary warming. Not only are all climate engineering elements highly toxic, but by chemically nucleating sea surfaces in the polar regions the climate engineers are actually preventing rapidly warming seas from releasing their heat. This in turn is further fueling the thawing of formerly frozen methane seabed deposits. The releasing methane then greatly contributes to feedback loops which, in turn, radically worsen the overall warming of the planet. Over a 10 year time horizon, methane is over 100 times more potent as a greenhouse gas than C02."
